                <h1>Peel and Stick Wallpaper: Top Tips & Tricks</h1>
                <p>Peel and stick wallpaper can transform your space effortlessly! Start with a clean, smooth surface for best adhesion. Measure and cut your panels carefully, allowing for pattern matching. Use a squeegee to smooth out air bubbles as you apply. For intricate edges, a utility knife works wonders. Enjoy your refreshed space!</p>
